node.text:
Super excited to announce the development of the @dbzcoin NFT marketplace 🎉 

Diamond Swap is the 1st #NFT marketplace to have a user friendly, easy to use, ticketing platform for musicians, along with a full marketplace experience where users can buy/sell/create NFT’s.

Unique to Diamond Swap, musicians will have a full platform where they be able to create a concert and sell tickets through NFT’s.

Alongside tickets, musicians will be able to sell digital merchandise and NFT’s for their concert in an easy to use all-in-one platform.

Diamond Swap will be Binance Smart Chain and Ethereum compatible. Users will be able to mint, import and sell NFT’s on both chains.

@dbzcoin will be the coin used for payments on the platform 💎

We will additionally look into adding #BSC, #ETH, and others.

More big news coming very soon 💎✊

Follow 👉 @dbzcoin 👈
